🧠 Debug Mode Kya Hota Hai?
Debug mode ka matlab:-
👉 System detailed logs generate kare
👉 Error ka root cause pata chale
👉 Workflow / Rule / Provisioning issue trace ho sake
Normal mode me sirf basic logs milte hain.
Debug mode me full internal processing logs milte hain 🔥

📂 Debug Logs Kahan Milte Hain?
Tomcat logs me:-
tomcat/logs/catalina.out
Ya:-
identityiq/log/

⚙️ Debug Mode Enable Kaise Kare?
IIQ me logging configuration file hoti hai:
identityiq/WEB-INF/classes/log4j.properties

🔹 Step 1: log4j.properties Open karo
Find karo:-
log4j.rootLogger=INFO, stdout

🔹 Step 2: INFO ko DEBUG me change karo
log4j.rootLogger=DEBUG, stdout

🔹 Specific Package Debug Enable Karna (Recommended)
Pure system ko DEBUG karna heavy hota hai ❗
Better hai specific package enable karo:-
Example:-
log4j.logger.sailpoint.api=DEBUG
log4j.logger.sailpoint.object=DEBUG
log4j.logger.sailpoint.provisioning=DEBUG
log4j.logger.sailpoint.workflow=DEBUG

🔹 Step 3: Tomcat Restart karo
startup.bat
Ya Linux:-
./startup.sh

🔍 Debug Mode Me Kya Dikhega?
Example scenarios:-
✅ Provisioning Issue
Request generate hua?
Plan create hua?
Connector call hua?
Error kya aaya?

✅ Workflow Issue
Kaunsa step execute hua?
Variable value kya thi?
Approval stuck kaha hua?

✅ Rule Debug
Agar BeanShell rule hai:-
log.debug("User name: " + identity.getName());
Ye DEBUG mode me print hoga.

🛑 Important Warning:-
Production me:-

❌ Full DEBUG mat chalao:-
Kyuki:-
Logs heavy ho jate hain
Performance impact hota hai
Disk space fill ho sakta hai
Sirf specific package debug karo.

🎯 Real Project Scenario:-

Issue:-
Access revoke nahi ho raha

Steps:-
1️⃣ Provisioning DEBUG enable
2️⃣ Logs check karo
3️⃣ Error milega:-
Connector issue?
Permission denied?
Mapping problem?

